{"tid":1822014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛以為自己成功帶到風向影大頭","createTime":"2020-01-12T16:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T16:34:44.000Z","uid":73959,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd2dea1720e01e481c6bbb773745fa4f5858580a","tid":1822014,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:26:59.000Z","msg":"又會一時間咁多人批鬥&rdquo;自己人&rdquo;去食藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又會突然不停玩輸民意icon<br />\n<br />\n其實你呢招唔係唔work㗎<br />\n不過衰在岀post出太密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同語氣太急進喇<br />\n有手足話你咁做唔好就起哂綱屌 做咩啫<br />\n<br />\n不過 呢個咪係真。手足同五毛嘅分別囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班五毛依然低賤 星期日都要開工<br />\n<br />\n你慢慢單機影啦 可能真係有人驚你影而唔去食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反正我哋會繼續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n想分化？想割？諗過第二條橋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae9a8ca17073ece9a95da37f430882317f202d8","tid":1822014,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:27:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足好珍貴<br />\n唔好再捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n愛國愛黨<br />\n咪嚟香港<br />\n<br />\n大人齊罷工<br />\n細路唔使衝</span></div>"},{"pid":"6c54a258f8443ce39b5dc0b2000436fc18807da7","tid":1822014,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:27:57.000Z","msg":"入嚟啦五毛 等緊你呀"},{"pid":"03c7f5a9115811c37c8d202e318feac158c2380a","tid":1822014,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:28:13.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d5fd089c5921454cd1e7473546b4be335cc17c","tid":1822014,"uid":28480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:28:1